item.title: CVE-2023-47164|2023-11-10T08:59:13.640Z -- digitaldruid.net -- hoteldruid
item.description: Cross-site scripting vulnerability in HOTELDRUID 3.0.5 and earlier allows a remote unauthenticated attacker to execute an arbitrary script on the web browser of the user who is logging in to the product.
